, it is also\nidentified that the pinch effect will be enhanced with the increase of\ndischarge power and the propulsion performance is promoted more distinctly. The\nmulti-anode APPT and the helixcoil multi-anode APPT have been proved to have\npotential application advantage in the field of micro-satellite propulsion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 29 Sep 2018 13:30:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Oct 2018 05:33:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2019 03:14:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-06"}
